	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f100135225589114><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=11&mid=100135225589114>Make big $ & EXP as a SOLO WIZ.</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=11&mid=100135225589114#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Sep 24th 1:24 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>As a high teen Wiz I will attest that many of the comments listed are true in regard to the need for SOW. Do what you can to get this on a regular basis in the form of boots or potions or a good Shm + Wiz group. Shammies are one of the best classes for a Wiz to group with due to the shareing of buffs and their ability to heal after battle and of coarse the SOW.<br>Now to make big cash quick and get nice Exp as a soloist;<br>1. Pick any zone with wil-o-wisps. QH,NK,WK all work well.(remember guards wont protect you from them so have a zone close or pull them to one if you think it's going to be dangerous) Then...<br>2. Useing a magic weapon like a staff easily found at the entrance to lake rathe but looting gnolls there. Sometimes higher lvl's will let you loot it anyway cause it's a lore item and they can only hold one anyhow. <br>3. Start with lightning at a distance usually you can get two shots off before it gets to you.then bash and blast till you get it.<br>4. The Exp is good but even better is the greater lightstone. This drops about 1 in 4 but sometimes you get luckier. <br>3. Give them to "marissa" or "mayala" or something like that in the gypsy camp by the guard tower in NK. She will give you a book you can sell back to her for 7pp a pop!!!!!<br>This stragity is a great way to get rich quick & lvl fast by yourself. Now lets hope some GM dont read this and change it/lol&nbsp;&nbsp;                                                     Strawberrie <br>"may the gavel of justice crush cowardly"<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
