	   <tr><td colspan=2>Frozen Mantle - Shoulder Slot - +10 MANA for like 20pp<br><br>Golden Ear Studs - +3 INT quest in qeynos/qeynos aquaducts<br><br>Gold Star Amulet - +4 INT jeweler made for like 75pp<br><br>Silver Rose Engagement Ring - +2 INT jeweler made for like 50pp or you may be able to find some moonstone rings that give some mana for about the same price.<br><br>Flowing Black Robe - +3 INT and some STR, 100pp<br><br>Dusty Bloodstained Gloves - +20 MANA I think, about 30-50pp<br><br>Polished Bone Bracelets - +3 INT +3 WIS, as cheap as 50pp sometimes<br><br>Dragoon Dirk - +3 SV MAGIC and something else, range slot weapon, 40pp<br><br>Skull of Jhen'tra - Off hand slot, gives you some extra mana 20pp or buy a Stein of Moggok - +10 INT for around 150-250pp<br><br>Runewood Totem Staff - Has some mana on it, Primary weapon slot for like 20pp<br><br>Braided Cinch Cord (+4 INT) or Gatorscale Arms (+4 INT) both sell for 250-450pp, buy one of those with whatever you have left over.<br><br>Your back slot can be quested, runescale cloak at lvl 25 or so.<br><br>Your face slot can be quested, acumen mask at lvl 30 or so.<br><br>Your runewood staff can be replaced by a Staff of the Wheel (quest) +10 INT as early as lvl 16.<br><br>Some things to remember - many great wizard items can be quested for.&nbsp;&nbsp;At early levels having +MANA items is much more beneficial than having +INT gear.<br><br>Fanie Fizzlebuns &lt;Desert Crane&gt;<br>31 Wizard on Bristlebane<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
