	   <tr><td colspan=2>I disagree. I don't think us having problems finding a group comes from a bad rep. I think it comes from groups being tank-centric. The tanks want healers and buffers, not nukers. Damage dealing is their job, they want people that can help them do what they do, not some one who can do it faster.<br><br>When I group, I find that many members are amazed by how fast the group is taking down mobs. With one nuke, I deal more damage in one round than 3 tanks put together. Few groups really appreciate what a good Wizard can do. Maybe because we a lumped into the damage dealer group, with the least amout of hitpoints.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
